OL,3,CWife mistakes husband's cardiac arrest
OL,4,Cfor snoring
OL,6,FA Basingstoke woman who was woken by
OL,7,Fher husband's loud snoring, says she
OL,8,Fwas unaware he was suffering a cardiac
OL,9,Farrest.
OL,11,FIt was only when Alison Crawford tried
OL,12,Fto encourage Barry to roll over, that
OL,13,Fshe realised something was terribly
OL,14,Fwrong.
OL,16,F"He was completely rigid when I nudged
OL,17,Fhim", remembers Alison. "I tried
OL,18,Fslapping his face to wake him up but
OL,19,Fthat didn't work and he continued
OL,20,Fmaking this very strange noise."
