OL,3,CWife mistakes husband's cardiac arrest
OL,4,Cfor snoring
OL,6,FIt was early in the morning of
OL,7,FNovember 7 last year, when Alison was
OL,8,Fwoken by Barry's loud snores.
OL,10,FThankfully, she realised something was
OL,11,Fwrong, and dialled 999.
OL,13,FRecognising the seriousness of Barry's
OL,14,Fsymptoms, emergency call taker Molly
OL,15,FMacguire talked Alison through how to
OL,16,Fcarry out CPR.
