OL,3,CWife mistakes husband's cardiac arrest
OL,4,Cfor snoring
OL,6,FNow recovered, he and Alison were keen
OL,7,Fto visit the medical staff who
OL,8,Ftogether saved his life.
OL,10,FThey have now visited the team face-to-
OL,11,Fface
OL,13,FBarry said: "It was important for me
OL,14,Fto come and say thank you to the
OL,15,Famazing team who saved my life and it
OL,16,Fwas a very special, and emotional,
OL,17,Fmeeting for Alison and I.
